{
  "id": "adv_event_2204_01_02",
  "title": "聴けば聴くほど",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "う～ん、レッスンの後のご飯は美味しいな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ the food after lessons is delicious‚ isn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 8.1426301956,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "分からないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't understand.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.3333333333,
      "endTime": 10.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "何が分からないんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What don't you understand?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.3333333333,
      "endTime": 12.2785487254,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "今回の企画、どうして琴乃やさくらじゃなくて\nすずが選ばれたのか、よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why was Suzu chosen instead of\nKotonoor Sakura for this project?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.4666666667,
      "endTime": 19.366666666700002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "私……ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.6,
      "endTime": 22.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "普通に考えるなら、妹の琴乃なり\n麻奈と縁の深いさくらが選ばれるのが妥当でしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Logically‚ it should be Kotono‚ Mana's sister‚ or Sakura‚\nwho has a deep connection with Mana‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.4666666667,
      "endTime": 29.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "その方が、テレビ的には話題性があるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That way‚ there would be more buzz and attention.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.4333333333,
      "endTime": 32.6809978326,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣はすずにゃんが猫っぽくて可愛いからかな\nって思ってたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe it's because Suzu-nyan is cute and cat-like.\nThat's what I thought.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.8666666667,
      "endTime": 38.1865703423,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そう思うのは芽衣だけですわ……\n私が星見プロで一番歌がうまいからに決まっています！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-that's only Mei's opinion…\nI was chosen because I'm the best singer at Hoshimi Pro!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.3666666667,
      "endTime": 47.5687126932,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "すずはまだまだこれからでしょう\n今この時点での歌唱力だけなら、もっと上はいるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu still has a long way to go.\nIf it's singing‚ there is better choice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.7666666667,
      "endTime": 54.515265055200004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "り、莉央さん？　すずだって、歌は上手で――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-Rio-san? Suzu is actually a skilled singer…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.7333333333,
      "endTime": 58.833333333300004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "確かに！　芽衣、瑠依ちゃんの歌聴きたいかも！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Exactly! Mei wants to hear Rui-chan's singing too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.9666666667,
      "endTime": 63.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっ、ちょっと芽衣まで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Wait‚ even Mei thinks so?…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.5,
      "endTime": 66.2272789955,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "あああなた達！　私に喧嘩を売っているんですわね！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Y-Y-Y-Y-You guys! Are you picking a fight with me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.4333333333,
      "endTime": 71.1999999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "そこまでおっしゃるのなら\n今回の仕事を立派にやり遂げて、証明してみせますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you're saying that‚\nthen I'll prove it by doing this job perfectly!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.5,
      "endTime": 78.05419179120001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "私が、一番、麻奈様の曲を歌いこなせるということを！\n次の伝説は、私、成宮すずがつくるということを！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll show that I'm the one who can master Mana-sama's songs the best!\nThe next legend will be created by me‚ Suzu Narumiya!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.2333333333,
      "endTime": 90.21,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "随分と大きく出たわね\n口だけにならないといいけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She's quite ambitious.\nI hope she's not just all talk.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.4666666667,
      "endTime": 95.2044514407,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "成宮家の人間たるもの、言った言葉に責任は持ちますわ\n今から特訓します！　芽衣、付き合って下さいまし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As a member of the Narumiya family‚ I take responsibility for my words.\nI'll start training from now on! Mei‚ please support me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.5,
      "endTime": 105.03333333340001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "いいよ～、これ食べ終わったら――って\n芽衣はまだ食べてるよーっ！　引っ張らないで～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure‚ after I finish eating…wait\nMei is still eating‚ don't pull me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.2333333333,
      "endTime": 114.9202662627,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、これであの子のステージが楽しみになったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ I'm looking forward to her stage now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.9666666667,
      "endTime": 121.1748752753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "え？　莉央さん、それはどういう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? R-Rio-san‚ what do you mean…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.3666666667,
      "endTime": 125.76773230239999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "あの子は暴走するくらい張り切った方が\n実力以上のパフォーマンスを出すものね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That girl performs better when she's driven to the edge.\nShe'll deliver a performance that exceeds her abilities…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.9666666667,
      "endTime": 131.5587181326,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、わざとですか？\nすずのこと、よく見てるんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you doing it on purpose?\nYou're observing Suzu closely‚ aren't you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.7666666667,
      "endTime": 138.0338459905,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "分かりやすい子だもの\nふふっ、すずには内緒よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She's an easy-to-read girl.\nHehe‚ let's keep it a secret from Suzu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.3333333333,
      "endTime": 142.635555549,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02(tokyosuzroom-00-noon)",
      "startTime": 143.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "まずは、お手本となる麻奈様の『Precious』を\nこのライブ映像で徹底的に研究するのですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "First‚ thoroughly study Mana-sama's \"Precious\"\nas a reference in this live performance video!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.8,
      "endTime": 152.6469357884,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02(tokyosuzroom-00-noon)",
      "startTime": 152.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "だね！　いっぱい聴いて完コピしようよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah! Let's listen many times and do a complete replication!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.8666666667,
      "endTime": 156.90000000010002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02(tokyosuzroom-00-noon)",
      "startTime": 157.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふ……もうすでに何千回も聴いているのですが\nさらに上を目指しますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehehe… I've already listened to it thousands of times‚\nbut I'll aim even higher.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.1666666667,
      "endTime": 164.1748219799,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02(tokyosuzroom-00-noon)",
      "startTime": 164.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんを驚かせてみせますわ！\nでは、麻奈様のライブを再生しますわよ！",
      "translations": {
